own.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n宜家返學都可以online上，點解拜神唔可以online拜？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T08:19:25.000Z","msg":"唔知關唔關呢單事<br />\n但韓國啲邪教好似幾大影響力"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T09:09:26.000Z","msg":"緊係啦連總統都係一份子<br />\n啲教會規模好大"},{"pid":"fcc9b6a38b7f7be5ec505e33b7513135a427648f","tid":1886890,"uid":38255,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T09:54:17.000Z","msg":"傳銷＋邪教<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1582089854.A.627.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FGossiping%2FM.1582089854.A.627.html&d=WZLdF6k3LRQ%2Bb7h5E4OoDlgnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=e0473fc1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1582089854.A.627.html</a><br />\n<br />\n目前都沒看到什麼記者在報 <br />\n<br />\n來分享一下，韓國人目前最憤怒的點是這位31號的韓國三寶（61歲，韓女） <br />\n她不只在直銷公司上班 （公司名稱：c-club，不是夜店，是直銷公司） 她去教會傳染了10個人，而那教會還是個邪教！ <br />\n這是韓國政府公布的路線：<a href=\"http://naver.me/xtFvDcUw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnaver.me%2FxtFvDcUw&d=WZLdF6k3LRQ%2Bb7h5E4OoDlgnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=dc3752f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://naver.me/xtFvDcUw</a> <br />\n<br />\n新天地耶穌教證據帳幕聖殿教會 <br />\n簡稱叫「新天地」，說是目前韓國三大邪教之一 <br />\n教主李萬熙是耶穌轉世（1931年生，89歲左右） 只有他看得懂聖經的意思。全韓國有12個支派"},{"pid":"aa780bf3c090f0afd5a04c06e7a05083e53603a7","tid":1886890,"uid":26601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T09:56:10.000Z","msg":"遍地開花，人民幣的代價<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91b33bf7441731960caf755355d0c7bacad586c7","tid":1886890,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T10:03:23.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}